description:
In this sample guitar lesson from his online guitar school, Andreas Oberg (http://artistworks.com/andreas-oberg) talks about jazz comping. This comes by special request from his online students, click on the link to find out more about online guitar lessons with Andreas Oberg!

Students of his online guitar school have unlimited access to hundreds of guitar lessons from Andreas, plus many other special performances and exclusive interviews. The best part though is that you can submit practice videos of yourself playing directly to the site for Andreas to review. He'll watch your video and respond with his own video where he tells you what you should be practicing in order to improve. All Andreas' students have access to each others' Video Exchanges®, which date back to 2009 so there are literally hundreds of them to go through. It's the most effective way to improve your playing - direct feedback from a master. Check out the link for more info about how it all works and to get more free sample lessons.
title: Guitar Lessons with Andreas Oberg: Jazz Comping
fulltitle: Guitar Lessons with Andreas Oberg: Jazz Comping
